casebody.data:
CITY OF SOUTHFIELD, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
JORDAN DEVELOPMENT COMPANY, LLC and Word of Faith Christian Center Church, Defendants-Appellees,
and
Department of Environmental Quality, Defendant. SC: 157220
COA: 333970 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 29, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 21, 2017 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
